<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((صحيح الادب المفرد)</span>) <span class="c2">(٧٢٩)</span>: ق.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>